highlights.text: “Tu Aake Dekhle” by King has been on Top Songs Mumbai the longest, at 65 weeks straight.
“Ghodey Pe Sawaar (From "Qala")” by Amit Trivedi, Amitabh Bhattacharya, and Sireesha Bhagavatula is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Mumbai, up 32 spots at #9.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Mumbai. “Kesariya” is the highest at #3.
“Ved Lavlay” by Ajay-Atul, Vishal Dadlani, and Ajay Gogavale is the highest new entry on Top Songs Mumbai at #65.
